ith the generalized Gutzwiller approximation in both AFM and\nparamagnetic states, and the results can be improved beyond the generalized\nGutzwiller approximation as the cluster is enlarged from a single site to 4\nsites. Our results demonstrate that the cluster slave-spin method can be a\npowerful tool to systematically investigate the strongly correlated system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jul 2017 20:04:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-12"}
