rce, finding a value of 7.6$\\pm 0.8$ kpc.\nFinally, we discuss the evolution of the system suggesting that it is\ncompatible with a conservative mass transfer driven by magnetic braking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2017 08:05:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
